<font class="option" color="#ffffff"><b><a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=26&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">TEH WIN!</a></b></font>
</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
<font class="content"><P align=center><FONT face=Arial><STRONG>Apparently no o­ne else will do this...<BR><BR>So had a great weekend in time, quick clear, all went smoothly.  <BR><BR>Quarm died, as I'm sure most that visit this sight already know, so here are your requested screenshots!<BR><BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/quarm_fight.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR><BR>Look at that evil beast....<BR><BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/quarm_corpse.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR><BR>But yet, he fell to the hands of the alliance.<BR><BR>We finally got the see the final script of PoP for us, which was rather intersting.<BR><BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/quarm1.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR><BR>So off to GoD we go and Plane of Time reaches </STRONG></FONT><FONT face=Arial><STRONG><EM>Farm Status.<BR><BR></EM>Last update for awhile I'm sure.<BR><BR></STRONG></FONT></P><br><br>
</font>
</td></tr></table>
