<font class="option" color="#ffffff"><b><a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=25&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">Endearing Time</a></b></font>
</td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
<font class="content"><P align=center><STRONG><FONT face=Arial>Everquest is a very unique game, people create goals in game to achieve and then work toward them.  Well The Alliance is that much closer to o­ne of them.  Our Plane of Time raid this weekend went very smooth, and the results were staggering.  Another new god dead, and we got to see o­ne nasty dragon type guy. His name? Quarm...<BR><BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/Quarmsmall.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR>Fighting Quarm at 2 A.M with a skeleton crew is a lot of fun!<BR><BR>To get to the big guy we had to overcome the man that has been keeping us back for two weeks.  Innoruuk.<BR><BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/innydead.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR><BR>Of course he dropped some loots.<BR><BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/jaggedblade.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR><FONT >Way To Go Fayde o­n our first JTB<BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/songbladeloot.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR></FONT><FONT >Grats Brilinnia o­n the Sword<BR><IMG alt="" hspace=0 src="http://homepages.wmich.edu/~j2cox/soa/shroudofsloot.jpg" align=baseline border=0><BR></FONT><FONT >And Grats to Yonyac o­n the new shoulders!<BR><BR><BR><FONT >That's all folks.....</FONT><BR></FONT></FONT></STRONG></P><br><br>
</font>
</td></tr></table>
